pan><hr size=1> Just reading the grab bag, and have posted the part below, and I cant help but think WTF. How many of us use faster, quicker weapons so that we have a better chance of disrupting a caster? I certainly was and then I read here that my weapon speed has no meaning what so ever, its based on your level. Whats most astounding to me is the comment:<br>
